{"tid":939134,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"南北戰爭","createTime":"2018-12-13T00:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T03:07:44.000Z","uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf84dbfedd83ae6814d872bc3ce76ed43e82886","tid":939134,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T00:55:06.000Z","msg":"睇左林肯搞呢場大龍鳳<br />\n但有幾個問題唔太明白<br />\n當年投票 中間有一堆州無參與<br />\n係因為無乜人住 定因爲未加入聯邦？<br />\n<br />\n當其時應該好多人都有黑奴<br />\n點解咁多人會支持林肯？<br />\n<br />\n又點解北面相比南面會咁多人支持解放黑奴？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/13/085320_93c9865be1c62ffafda68f7947ded2c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F085320_93c9865be1c62ffafda68f7947ded2c8.png&h=551b10f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f11d0a423374707b7b206d9bcdc7b6fc2f4fddf2","tid":939134,"uid":126960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"如果單指解放黑奴呢樣野 其實睇番當時南北經濟模式就知<br />\n北方係主要集中喺比較高科技嘅產業 而南方就係種植園 <br />\n咁當然南方人緊係支持畜奴 唔係搵鬼種 而北方人就可以企喺道德高地支持廢奴<br />\n<br />\n利申：識少少 拋個磚 順便留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c565d98aa66c59efba24709395b824f4b90389a2","tid":939134,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64854c9f23c55c15bbf32033d0172a361b162385","tid":939134,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"「老李」雖然係南軍，但佢似乎唔係好撐黑奴制度，佢臨死前亦立遺囑要歸還自由畀佢屋企嘅黑奴同佢嘅仔女<br />\n<br />\n留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10da4901b2125359c48d06e81b61db906b07106d","tid":939134,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"南方氣候溫暖適合種棉花、煙草<br />\n所以南方要用黑人，北方唔洗"},{"pid":"2b19c79306fda556570fbba04d76c5dad96d1af6","tid":939134,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"當其時應該好多人都有黑奴<br />\n點解咁多人會支持林肯？<br />\n<br />\n因為獨立戰爭已經將自由概念植入美國人內心"},{"pid":"ba59ab63a97ca855b1bfad2bab84f4c09fe9c183","tid":939134,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪想擴大生產力同增加內需？奴隸做嘢應該冇咁落力 同因為收入低/冇收入所以消費能力唔高 但解放咗之後有國民身分就會帶動內需同增加稅收 which are有利於北方州份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申鳩噏"},{"pid":"78e4ed77f0aee114edbae9d3a4e6e405fd4a774d","tid":939134,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"有無人知中間d州點解無份投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482f0d9212d06a389f57f5a48922a0fbbd9ff176","tid":939134,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78e4ed77f0aee114edbae9d3a4e6e405fd4a774d","tid":939134,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"有無人知中間d州點解無份投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"開發程度未夠?<br />\n西進運動D人會優先發展西岸?"},{"pid":"7bace822902217f001a122ed7a050bc3f55cd033","tid":939134,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"482f0d9212d06a389f57f5a48922a0fbbd9ff176","tid":939134,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78e4ed77f0aee114edbae9d3a4e6e405fd4a774d","tid":939134,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"有無人知中間d州點解無份投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"開發程度未夠?<br />\n西進運動D人會優先發展西岸?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"而唔係發展美國中部"},{"pid":"4ac7fc584b7240d0d37c9fd3d1e01493f5cb5474","tid":939134,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo